{"url": "https://www.slo.courts.ca.gov/sh/selfhelp-conservatorship.htm", "_type": "index", "body": ["<p>Visit the California Courts website to get an understanding on appointing a responsible person or organization to care for another adult.\n\n<strong>Do It Yourself</strong>\n\n<p>We have a document preparation program available for you to use to complete the necessary forms to request a limited conservatorship. This program will ask you to answer questions that are needed to request a limited conservatorship. The answers you give will be used to complete the forms needed to request a limited conservatorship.&nbsp; This program&nbsp;will also&nbsp;allow you to print out&nbsp;all the completed necessary forms.</p>\n\n<p>Get Started</p></p>"], "_template": "5a0b-4d51-805f", "parent": ["https://www.slo.courts.ca.gov/sh/index.htm"], "title": ["Limited Conservatorship"]}
{"url": "https://www.slo.courts.ca.gov/sh/selfhelp-guardianship.htm", "_type": "index", "body": ["<p>Guardianship is a court proceeding in which a judge gives someone who is not the parent, custody of a child, or the power to manage the child's property (called \"estate\"), or both.\n\n<p>You may&nbsp;obtain more information about guardianship, alternatives to guardianship, duties of a guardian, becoming a guardian and ending a guardianship.<br/>\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n<strong>Guardianship Video</strong>\n\n<p>We show this helpful video to all people interested in learning more about the court process to obtain a guardianship.&nbsp; Contra Costa County courts provide the videos, but apply equally as well to San Luis Obispo.</p>\n\n<p>The full video is about 30 minutes.&nbsp;Click here to watch the video: Guardianship Video<br/>\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n<strong>Instructions and Sample Forms</strong>\n\n<p>You may click on the following link to view instructions and a&nbsp;sample of&nbsp;completed forms:&nbsp;Instructions and Sample Forms</p>\n\n<strong><br/>\nNeed Filing Help?</strong>\n\n<p>Request Guardianship</p>\n\n<p></p></p>"], "_template": "5a0b-4d51-805f", "parent": ["https://www.slo.courts.ca.gov/sh/index.htm"], "title": ["Guardianship"]}
