a holiday falls on a Saturday, the preceding Friday will be observed as a holiday.</p></p>"], "_template": "5a0b-4d51-805f", "parent": ["https://www.slo.courts.ca.gov/gi/index.htm"], "title": ["Court Holidays"]}
{"url": "https://www.slo.courts.ca.gov/gi/index.htm", "_type": "index", "body": ["<strong>ADA</strong>\r\n            \r\n\r\n<p>Access for all citizens.</p>\r\n\r\n    <p>MORE &raquo;</p>\r\n\r\n\t\r\n\t\r\n         \r\n \r\n\r\n                <strong>Contact Info &amp; Locations</strong>\r\n            \r\n\r\n<p>Where to find us.</p>\r\n\r\n    <p>MORE &raquo;</p>\r\n\r\n\t\r\n\t\r\n         \r\n \r\n\r\n                <strong>Court Calendars</strong>\r\n            \r\n\r\n<p>View our courtroom schedules.</p>\r\n\r\n    <p>MORE &raquo;</p>\r\n\r\n\t\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\t\r\n         \r\n \r\n\r\n                <strong>Court Holidays</strong>\r\n            \r\n\r\n<p>Court holiday closures for the calendar year.</p>\r\n\r\n    <p>MORE &raquo;</p>\r\n\r\n\t\r\n\t\r\n         \r\n \r\n\r\n                <strong>Reporter Transcripts</strong>\r\n            \r\n\r\n<p>How to request transcripts.</p>\r\n\r\n    <p>MORE &raquo;</p>\r\n\r\n\t\r\n\t\r\n         \r\n \r\n\r\n                <strong>Employment</strong>\r\n            \r\n\r\n<p>Working for the Superior Court in San Luis Obispo.</p>\r\n\r\n    <p>MORE &raquo;</p>\r\n\r\n\t\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\t\r\n         \r\n \r\n\r\n                <strong>Interpreter Services</strong>\r\n            \r\n\r\n<p>Find a court interpreter.</p>\r\n\r\n    <p>MORE &raquo;</p>\r\n\r\n\t\r\n\t\r\n         \r\n \r\n\r\n                <strong>Jury Services</strong>\r\n            \r\n\r\n<p>Information about this time honored service plus frequently asked questions.</p>\r\n\r\n    <p>MORE &raquo;</p>\r\n\r\n\t\r\n\t\r\n         \r\n \r\n\r\n                <strong>Media</strong>\r\n            \r\n\r\n<p>How the media can contact the court for permission to film or record in a courtroom.</p>\r\n\r\n    <p>MORE &raquo;</p>\r\n\r\n\t\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\t\r\n         \r\n \r\n\r\n                <strong>Scam Alerts</strong>\r\n            \r\n\r\n<p>If you receive an email referencing a \"Notice to Appear in Court\", please delete it immediately. San Luis Obispo Superior will never email a Notice to Appear in Court to the public.</p>\r\n\r\n    <p>MORE &raquo;</p>"], "_template": "5a0b-4d51-805f", "parent": ["https://www.slo.courts.ca.gov/"], "title": ["General Information"]}
